imdb.plot outline: Daniel Bellmore, is a somewhat comfortable actor who is still struggling to make his mark in the industry and make his life mean something. He is a husband and father and brother to an optimistic if unrealistic brother. We follow him, mocumentary style, in his day to day life to catch a glimpse into the life of a working actor.
imdb.title: The Actor's Life
plot: Juggling family, career and a ridiculous brother, it's a laugh a minute as Daniel Bellmore tries to keep it all together. He's an actor, he's been on the cusp of a big breakthrough several times, but home runs aren't scored on near misses.::North Hollywood
